<div class="inner_heading"><span class="brown">Our Vision &amp; Mission</span></div><h2></h2>
<p><strong>Mission Statement:</strong></p>

<p>MDT Lubes’ mission is to offer safe, efficient and environmental friendly technology coupled with being a provider of cost effective friction reducing solutions. We understand India, and are committed towards providing solutions suitable for its extreme weather conditions. MDT Lubes is committed towards ensuring the optimum consumer satisfaction in all the markets we serve. MDT Lubes intends to build a strong network of distribution channels, thereby ensuring that the demands arising from every corner of the country are met.  MDT Lubes is committed in ensuring the growth of our partners, whom we understand to be an integral part of our business.</p>

<p><strong>Vision:</strong></p>

<p>MDT Lubes thrives to be the global leader in grease and lubricants industry; we have a dedicated passionate team working round the clock to achieve this goal. We are committed towards building an entity that contributes in growth and development of the nation, focussing especially on the development at the grass root level. </p>

<p><strong>Our Values:</strong></p>

<p style="text-align:justify !important;"> We believe in building long term relationship with our customers and in career growth for our staff.<br />
1.	Integrity and Honesty;<br />
2.	Respect;<br />
3.	Corporate Responsibility; <br />
4.	Social Responsibility;<br />
5.	Excellence ; and<br />
6.	Learning.<br />
                     </p>
    <p><strong> Quality:</strong></p>

    <p>has always been the top most priority of MDT Lubes, and we are always committed in providing the best experience to all our consumers. MDT Lubes, through its excellent customer service, reliability and technologically innovative products, has pledged towards providing a flawless customer experience. MDT Lubes is forever committed to ensure that the quality of its products and services remains high. There are strict quality control and management processes put in place to ensure that products that display the MDT brand are consistently of the highest quality. The same is also demonstrated in the high standard of service and care that is offered to its customers. MDT products are compliant with all latest industry standards (API, ACEA, JASO etc); we have ISO accredited blending plants, Technical partnership with Pride International Lubricants Company, LLC Ajman (U.A.E) which reflects upon our commitment towards bringing the latest technological advancement around the world to the Indian Market, and to provide with the highest international standards in Lubricants.  </p>


    <p><strong> Passion:</strong></p>

    <p> towards manufacturing, friction reducing products, and catering to needs of the Indian domestic industry is the driving force behind MDT Lubes. With a team of professionals having more than 30 years of experience in this field, MDT Lubes promises to reach greater heights in the coming years. We believe that it is this zeal and determination within every member of MDT Lubes that helps us serve you better and cater to the requirements of the Indian Lubricants market. Nothing motivates us more than catering to your requirements to the best of your satisfaction.</p>


